\chapter*{Beast Template}                                                                                                                                                                                                              
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                       
This template is designed to help you create a beast for Dungeons & Dragons 5th Edition using LaTeX and Bookdown.                                                                                                                      
                                                                                                                                                                                                                                       
