**Beast Description**

Insert a brief description of the beast, including its habits, habitat, and any notable features or behaviors.

\end{document}

This template provides basic structure for your beast, with sections for:

* Beast statistics (armor class, hit points, speed)
* Abilities
* Attacks and traits
* Lair and environment
